仿，也列上U11的防水級數，但英國廣告標準委員會認為，警語標示不夠明確，廣告有誇大不實和誤導成份在，下令廣告全面下架。"},{"pid":"d6a2fb3fa38e0ceadc08de0f66c5114c34939e46","tid":622881,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T23:40:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"075d7c828c2f0d614214aa3f8b018cbc1f0ae274","tid":622881,"uid":30179,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d6a2fb3fa38e0ceadc08de0f66c5114c34939e46","tid":622881,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"a16d224035fab0610a748a5c87025a8ff2974086","tid":622881,"uid":12628,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">買</span></span>乜撚野廣告？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T23:40:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T23:41:59.000Z","msg":"點睇都係買廣告時段賣廣告<br />\n連登d小學雞仲未返學？"},{"pid":"2d3f97dea8558a95ec6e086cb516af9b50967794","tid":622881,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:01:16.000Z","msg":"仲邊有錢，收入得個8億幾港元，都唔知夠唔夠俾營運成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宏達電3月營收再跌破30億 等旗艦機救援<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/3067796\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5641%2F3067796&d=wjlpzYbn174bK8wge4s9nP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6173c8b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/3067796</a>"},{"pid":"eb82e7beeaf6e896297b20c85ab957545c8a171d","tid":622881,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:37:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35cea70b31a22f27b3f5b5dca303a30a012a6c4b","tid":622881,"uid":8717,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2d3f97dea8558a95ec6e086cb516af9b50967794","tid":622881,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:01:16.000Z","msg":"仲邊有錢，收入得個8億幾港元，都唔知夠唔夠俾營運成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa